2x^2 + 7x + 3
2x   ->     3
*           *
x    ->     1

(2x * 3) + (x * 1) = 6x + x = 7x ! matches
now write cross thing
(2x+1) * (x+3) -> this is how you factor this quadratic polynomial
(2x)(x) + (2x)(3) + (1)(x) + (1)(3) = 2x^2 + 6x + x + 3 = 2x^2 + 7x +3 !

EX:
6x^2+49x+ 8
to factor
6x        8  48x
 x        1  x
             49x
6x^2+14x+ 8
oR
2x        4 8x
3x        2 6x
            14x !
multiply cross
(2x+2)(3x+4)

